summary: SummaryHighlightsSustainable PackagingWear confidence. EstÃ©e Lauder Double Wear Stay-in-Place Makeup is a 24-hour liquid foundation with a flawless, natural, matte finish that helps to unify uneven skin tone and control oil and shine. Buildable medium-to-full coverage in over 55 shades.
details: DetailsBenefits24-hour staying power: EstÃ©e Lauder's #1 foundation worldwide.Double Wear is the makeup that keeps up, no touch-ups needed.Finish: Fresh matte.Coverage: Medium to full, buildable.24-hour wear.24-hour color true.24-hour non-creasing.Oil-free. Controls oil all day.Sweat-, heat- and humidity-resistant. Waterproof. Lifeproof.No caking, no settling into fine lines or pores, no poring, no streaking.Feels lightweight and so comfortable, you won't believe it's long wear.In a wide range of shades that flatters all. Won't look grey on deeper skintones.Won't cause breakouts, won't clog pores (non-acnegenic).Dermatologist-tested.Free of synthetic fragrance.Formulated WithoutFree of synthetic fragrance Gluten-free Free of parabens, phthalates, sulfites, drying alcohols, mineral oil - and animal-derived ingredientsItem 2309420How To UseUsing fingertips, sponge or foundation brush, smooth over skin. Start at center of face and blending outward. Add a little more to build it as a full coverage foundation.PRO TIPS: Shake well, and allow any liquid foundation to dry completely before confirming it's your perfect shade. And always test it on your face (not your arm or wrist) for the most accurate results.IngredientsWater\Aqua\Eau, Cyclopentasiloxane, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, PEG/PPG-18/18 Dimethicone, Butylene Glycol, Tribehenin, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Magnesium Sulfate, Tocopheryl Acetate, Polymethylsilsesquioxane, Methicone, Laureth-7, Xanthan Gum, Alumina, Sodium Dehydroacetate, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Cellulose Gum, Propylene Carbonate, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-Di-T-Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Phenoxyethanol. May Contain: Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Mica, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891).Please be aware that ingredient lists may change or vary from time to time. Please refer to the ingredient list on the product package you receive for the most up to date list of ingredients.Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Using fingertips, sponge or foundation brush, smooth over skin. Start at center of face and blending outward. Add a little more to build it as a full coverage foundation.PRO TIPS: Shake well, and allow any liquid foundation to dry completely before confirming it's your perfect shade. And always test it on your face (not your arm or wrist) for the most accurate results.

reviews.headline: it doesn't perform as well as my old bottle of DW :(
reviews.comments: something definitely changed with this formula and I'm so disappointed. I have an old bottle from a few years back that I wanted to replace, but the difference in performance is wild. It used to be amazing for oil control and now it breaks up so easily, something it never did before. doublewear is the only foundation I used until now and I wanted to use it forever!

reviews.headline: Detailed shade range & long lasting
reviews.comments: This is a versatile coverage product, would be perfect for a long lasting light to medium coverage or can be layered to build coverage. It has a very thin consistency making it difficult to cover scaring and acne marks but lasts & is rather dewy.

reviews.headline: Amazing Foundation!
reviews.comments: Love this foundation! One of the only ones that holds up to my super oily skin. It doesn't bother me at all that the bottle doesn't have a pump. It is much better without. I don't waste any product!

reviews.headline: I would buy this a million times
reviews.comments: Amazing foundation. Perfect color. Lasts all day. Didn't oxidize much.

reviews.headline: Great coverage
reviews.comments: Great coverage, can be used any season, all skin types

reviews.headline: Best out there
reviews.comments: I've been using this foundation for years, and haven't found anything I like better. I've tried 10+ other high-end foundations, and always come back to this one. It stays on all day without smudging, doesn't transfer, covers blemishes without looking cakey, and doesn't settle into fine lines. I use one pump for more of an everyday look, but can layer if I want more of a "full glam". One bottle also lasts me for months. Highly recommend!

reviews.headline: It looks just like skin, not cakey
reviews.comments: This is matte, meaning it looks like your natural skin, so if you want a bit of glow use a glowy primer and setting spray/powder. Also its very full coverage so take a little bit and use a damp sponge it easily blends out while also giving good coverage with a little bit. Stayed all day like it says. Usually used NYX serum concealer as a foundation but this staus a lot better and its a lot less cakey

faceoff_positive.comments: I have a hard skin tone to match, I have always struggled with finding a good makeup for my oily-combination skin. After trying many brands and creams I was told to try this product. I went in to get a tone match and found the perfect one. This stuff stays on all day and I hardly have to touch up anymore. It is really good for my uneven skin tone as well. Definitely recommend for anyone looking for a good coverage foundation!
faceoff_positive.headline: Best makeup!

faceoff_negative.comments: I have been using this product literally since the week it was released. 20 years plus ago? The formula was PERFECT. The shade Shell, was PERFECT. The formula has been changed ( and no longer has sunscreen ) and does not go on or stay on the way the old formula did. The shade Shell was originally replaced with a drugstore orange shade, but they keep testing new shades. All of them horrible. When they first changed the formula and dropped this very popular shade, the reviews were terrible. It went from a 5 Star product and kept dropping. It seems like the Review counter has been reset. It appears to me that Estee is starting over with new reviews by consumers who aren't familiar with how good the OLD formula was so they have no idea how awful this formula is compared to that. I had been a very loyal Estee customer. All my makeup and skincare products were Estee. BTW Double Wear Foundation in the original Shell shade is still available in Great Britain and can be ordered from better online British retailers.Now Estee has dropped Lucidity loose powder and many customers are trying to use Double Wear powder foundation as a replacement. Don't waste your money. It works nothing like Lucidity powder.The Lucidity pressed powder doesn't work like the loose powder did either.
faceoff_negative.headline: What happened to all the OTHER reviews for this?
